- xmlstarlet, json_pp, yamllint, tomlq, hjson
- archive, zip, 7z, xz
- svn, hg, darcs, fossil, bzr, cvs
- pacman, dnf, zypper, emerge, apk, pkg, nix-env, guix, spack, pkgsrc

